channel.title: What was your first track EVER?
channel.description:
I know there is already a topic which says your first Auxy track, but I’m talking about what was the first song you ever made (online or in an app).
Just post a link :smiley: Here’s mine:
https://soundation.com/user/DeliEatsAHotDog/track/fortronic
I had changed my name to LimeZ just because I wanted to :P (My first name was Trasx, then DubbTrasx (which was my SoundCloud for a while), then others like Jetpack, Venomous, and then...Delphi, and...well I had a lot (don’t post your previous names [if you had any]).
